Run ChatSystem1 project first
After that run ChatSystem 
Here ChatSystem1 is  written as server code
And ChatSystem is written  as client code
To run this application the operating system must be windows(any version) and E:\\ disk must be in system 
If any other operating system is used then to run this application a little bit change in code is required->
(1) change the value of path variable in files
(a)SignIn.java(line---14)
(b)forgetPassword.java(line---11)
(c)CreateAccount.java(line---55)
(d)changePassword.java(line---11)
in both(ChatSystem and ChatSystem1) projects
